{"tid":2023221,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本土派入嚟，熱狗係你嘅敵人","createTime":"2020-05-19T00:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T03:32:54.000Z","uid":78768,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c692529a76aed55b3072f91ebceca7382b5d4830","tid":2023221,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"喂，千祈唔好覺得熱狗屌泛民就係同路人，事實上本土派應該比泛民更憎熱狗，因為熱狗算係間接搞散咗新東補選後嘅本土派。<br />\n<br />\n當日天琦講完三分天下，第二日即刻走出黎話五區參選、然後屌本民前endorse青政係冇政治倫理、選輸就開清算list、梁游DQ第一時間出嚟恥笑、之後開始帶頭屌港大幫、青政、盧斯達、本民前，話天琦係西瓜琦，跟本上熱狗嘅分化就係令本土派響近年搞唔起嘅主因。<br />\n<br />\n各位，如果你叫開「光復香港、時代革命」口號、鍾意唱「願榮光歸香港」、有拉過人鏈、食過黃店、有戴過口罩，你已經係熱血公民嘅敵人。<br />\n<br />\n因為熱狗會1. 屌人叫「光復香港、時代革命」口號，認為叫「驅逐共黨、光復香港」或「天滅中共」等先係對準政權；2.屌人唱「願榮光歸香港」，稱其難聽，僭越上帝，認為「城邦之歌」先係真正代表香港；3.嘲諷香港之路手拖手人鏈活動係「像奴隸一樣穿在一起」；4.批評黃色經濟圈，認為係抹殺個人自由，只懂批鬥，但自己正建立「好人經濟圈」；5.一直咬定武漢肺炎由實驗室製造，是中共生產，但其後稱病毒「廢過感冒」、「不用鳩戴口罩」，認為戴口罩無助防疫，推崇無科學根據的銀離子水消毒。<br />\n<br />\n認同本土價值，支持本土理念嘅同道，鄭松泰好早已經講咗佢哋係「扮本土派」，因為「大眾係白痴」，你又會唔會比佢哋昆到？"},{"pid":"e12a6b666454987fea6fba8b6f21602ae787737b","tid":2023221,"uid":198373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"同意，我係本土獨派，憎呢班打靶狗多過林鄭政權"},{"pid":"9937a91ab6efdcd527354f9d4a127f15955b447d","tid":2023221,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5b5e823ff5386d52287c45d8acced31061dae975","tid":2023221,"uid":281584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"唔好再比熱狗話自己係本土,扮曬大台<br />\n真本土要壯大自己攞返話語權"},{"pid":"d4a4b5bbfb1ccd01c82b0e88a2d52e2e432d0e6a","tid":2023221,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"令我諗返起 國民黨同共產黨內亂既畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8023bf7e761bdfedc3a73ea9c1273dda609e1c31","tid":2023221,"uid":41846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T01:40:53.000Z","msg":"成班熱狗都被陳雲呃咗啦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2022642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2022642</a>"},{"pid":"308d77998bc2caeeaee91227d90d3be411a10ae2","tid":2023221,"uid":89030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"佢地唔當我地係同路人，我地同樣毋須爆當佢地係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a928d243afc7a415defd8cc2e60489abb2868a","tid":2023221,"uid":41846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:28:05.000Z","msg":"CLS，陳雲佢幫人，擺明想獨佔本土大台，<br />\nDLLM，成本城邦論口講香港建國，<br />\n實質上想推中共成為共主嚟成立華夏聯邦，<br />\n根本完全唔係脫中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59357626fdff839557f94c8137bee1584c0c90d2","tid":2023221,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2FwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=aa2240d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【612基金】<span style=\"color: orange;\">大量手足上庭，基金只剩幾三千萬！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://612fund.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fdonate&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2FwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=58cdc342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://612fund.hk/donate</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【星火】<span style=\"color: oran